{
  "captions": [
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- I can see why that may be.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:19.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Would you be happy to explain more</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:22.679"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>and we can interpret for you?</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:25.159"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Sure, I want my child\nto come into the world</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:28.480"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>full of breath, life, a\nhealthy baby, Deaf or hearing.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:34.440"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>But also, it would be funny to say</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:41.360"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I hadn't thought about\nraising a Deaf child.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:44.039"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I would be lying.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:46.519"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I'm Deaf.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:48.840"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I have a beautiful life.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:50.639"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>As a child growing up\nin the 80s, it was hard.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:57.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>My environment was very hearing,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:02.559"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>family, school, and I just\ndidn't know how to be me.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:05.639"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>In a world that every\nday taught me, told me</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:13.840"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>because I wasn't hearing\nthere was a fault with me.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:18.840"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>That was wrong.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:22.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>But eventually I found my tribe, friends,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:27.400"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>my culture, the Deaf community.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:30.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>That's the beauty of my world.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:34.039"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I know that to have and\nto raise a Deaf child,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:36.639"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>they can have that too.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:40.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- Surely we can't allow that.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:44.480"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- Why not?</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:47.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- Because you'd be making it deaf.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:49.039"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- And? You're missing the point.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:52.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>A child is a child.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:56.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>A Deaf child can really soar at life.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:58.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- This really is madness.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:03.159"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- You don't understand.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:06.360"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>But even that's a bit much.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:07.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- I think it goes without saying</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:11.400"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>that I'm for parental choice,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:12.639"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>but it has to be\nquestioned if it conflicts</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:14.400"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>with the right of the\nchild to an open future.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:17.960"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Put simply, what if the child grows up</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:21.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>and no longer wants to be deaf?</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:24.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- I'll tell you what.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:27.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>The parent would've messed\nthe child up. That's what.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:28.639"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- Harmed, I think is the more\nappropriate language here.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:31.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- Harmed? I would never.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:34.599"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- I'm sure you wouldn't mean to,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:37.280"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>but if they grew up not wanting to be deaf</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:38.719"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>and that was a decision\nthat you had made for them,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:42.719"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>then unfortunately there's\nprobably no other way</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:46.039"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>of describing it.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:49.000"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- Your response is typical, expected.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:51.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Everything up to this point that I said</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:55.559"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>about my lived experience,\nwhy I want a Deaf child,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:57.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>has gone in one ear and out the other.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:03.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Perhaps you're just not ready\nfor this type of conversation.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:07.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I understand.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:13.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I know that it is not for you,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:16.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>but would you be happy for\nme to describe deafness</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:18.920"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>as an impairment?</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:22.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Your words.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:27.440"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Would you consider using this technology</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:36.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>to ensure your child had a trait</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:40.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>that others may consider an\nimpairment such as deafness?</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:43.559"
    }
  ]
}